snippet: The Vancouver Canucks sent the star goalie Roberto Luongo back to the Florida Panthers.
abstract: NHL Roundup; several standout players are transferred in final day before NHL trade deadline; Vancouver Canucks trade goalie Robert Luongo and forward Steven Anthony to the Florida Panthers for goalie Jacob Markstrom and forward Shawn Matthias; other hockey news noted.
lead_paragraph: The Vancouver Canucks sent the star goalie Roberto Luongo back to the Florida Panthers.

headline.main: Luongo Is Biggest Name on Busy Day of Trades
headline.print_headline: Luongo Is Biggest Name on Busy Day of Trades
